{"tid":2442480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何柱國：倘林鄭競逐連任 他會考慮陪跑 爲港商當面屌柒佢都不錯","createTime":"2021-03-11T11:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T11:27:36.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d36c34251a44c5b7727805d8f68aedfa89b3a08b","tid":2442480,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:26:07.000Z","msg":"何柱國：倘林鄭月娥競逐連任　他會考慮參選特首 <br />\n<br />\n全國政協常委何柱國表示，如果特首林鄭月娥競逐連任，他會考慮參選行政長官。何柱國表示，不認同林鄭月娥曾經表示自己建設多於破壞的講法，如果林鄭月娥再參選，他一定出來找個機會與她辯論，表示「想看看她建設了甚麼」。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382591&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=7629efac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382591</a>"},{"pid":"aff9c6df63862dad9d3339f634b7910342317b89","tid":2442480,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:27:36.000Z","msg":"咁重口味？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}